org.mybatis.spring.boot.test.autoconfigure

Annotation Type AutoConfigureMybatis


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Documented
 @Inherited
 @ImportAutoConfiguration
public @interface AutoConfigureMybatis
    Auto-configuration imports for typical Mybatis tests. Most tests should consider using @MybatisTest rather than using this annotation directly.
    Since:
    1.2.1
    Author:
    wonwoo
